[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":85},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fen\u002Fjsweirdworld\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F25\u002Fjs-weird-world-68-the-end-is-a-new-beginning\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fen\u002Fjsweirdworld\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F25\u002Fjs-weird-world-68-the-end-is-a-new-beginning\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fen\u002Fjsweirdworld\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F25\u002Fjs-weird-world-68-the-end-is-a-new-beginning\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fen\u002Fjsweirdworld\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F25\u002Fjs-weird-world-68-the-end-is-a-new-beginning\u002F":67,"related:\u002Fen\u002Fjsweirdworld\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F25\u002Fjs-weird-world-68-the-end-is-a-new-beginning\u002F":76},"\u002Fjsweirdworld\u002F20190525\u002F3343743369\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":49,"date":50,"description":51,"extension":52,"lang":53,"meta":54,"navigation":55,"path":56,"readingMinutes":57,"seo":58,"standalone":59,"stem":60,"tags":61,"tldr":64,"updated":50,"url":65,"__hash__":66},"content\u002Fen\u002FJsWeirdWorld\u002Fjs-weird-world-68-the-end-is-a-new-beginning.md","[JS Weird World] No.68 Wrapping Up the Weird Parts of JavaScript","1000506819",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":43},"minimark",[11,16,24,27,30,34],[12,13,15],"h2",{"id":14},"an-ending-is-just-another-beginning","An Ending Is Just Another Beginning",[17,18,19],"p",{},[20,21],"img",{"alt":22,"src":23},"Image","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FWDhXvqd.png",[17,25,26],{},"Finishing up the weird parts of JavaScript feels like I finally kept a promise to myself — to keep learning. But an ending is always just another beginning, so maybe I'll come back later, dig out the bits I'm still a bit fuzzy on, and write them down again.",[17,28,29],{},"Honestly, I'm really grateful for everything this course taught me. It gave me a whole new way of thinking about concepts I thought I already understood. So if you ask me whether I'd recommend it — yeah, I would. The course is a little dated, sure, but a lot of the ideas in it are st